						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Vash wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">When is frame rendered?</div>
<br />The PPU is constantly working alongside the CPU. It keeps repeating this cycle: 20 Vblank scanlines, 1 dummy scanline, 240 picture scanlines, 1 dummy scanline. It never stops. It's the responsibility of the game program to sync itself to this cycle.</div>

