					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Ok so the CPU and PPU are working in parallel but in my emulator I wanted to do something that looks like a game loop as this : 
<br />
<br />while(GAME_RUNNING)
<br />{
<br />   if(timeElapsed&gt;=tick)
<br />        Game.update();
<br />
<br />   Game.render();
<br />}
<br />
<br />So basically my question is when do I stop the CPU emulator to render a frame?</div>

