					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There are 262 scanlines, but 341 PPU cycles in each scanline.  More like 89342 PPU cycles total (29780.66... CPU cycles).
<br />
<br />You need to expect the game to write to the PPU during rendering time, because even Super Mario Bros changes the scrolling location part way through draw time.</div>

					
